```

### 打字效果
```css
@keyframes typing {
  from { width: 0 }
  to { width: 100% }
}

.typing-animation {
  display: inline-block;
  overflow: hidden;
  white-space: nowrap;
  animation: typing 3s steps(40, end);
}
```

### 扫描线
```css
@keyframes scan {
  0% { transform: translateY(-100%); }
  100% { transform: translateY(100%); }
}

.scan-effect {
  position: absolute;
  top: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  height: 5px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, transparent, theme('colors.cyan.400'), transparent);
  animation: scan 2s linear infinite;
  opacity: 0.5;
}
```

